div.h1: Leading Provider of Comprehensive SAP Services
div.p: Take your business to the next level with our best SAP consulting and implementation services. Customised to what your business needs for efficiency in operations and scale. Begin your digital transformation journey today.

SAP business one offers a licensing structure designed to provide access to its ERP software, ensuring secure and efficient use of company data. Licences are distributed through authorised partners rather than directly from SAP, to ensure that users receive the necessary training and support.

div.span: This model offers unlimited access to the software for a one-time fee, allowing installation on the company's premises. It represents a significant initial investment and does not cover future software updates. To access updates, a maintenance fee, typically 17% of the software cost, is required annually.

Under this model, users pay a recurring fee (monthly or yearly) for the right to use the software, which is hosted remotely. This fee includes maintenance and support, but the licence must be renewed according to the subscription plan to continue access.

p.span: This structure ensures that businesses can tailor the software access according to the specific needs and roles of their users, enhancing efficiency and data security.
